title: Stunning Studio in the Heart of Belltown!
posting_body: ['Skye at Belltown', 'Property Address', '500 Wall Street', 'Seattle, WA, 98121', '<URL>', 'Skye at Belltown Apartments is one of Seattle’s most iconic apartment communities, soaring 18 stories above the Belltown neighborhood with really - and this is no exaggeration - the most stunning views.', 'That is, if you think the Space Needle is cool to gaze at.', 'Or the downtown skyline.', 'Or the sunsets.', "Then there's the expansive rooftop garden, with lush green space and multiple social zones.", "Meanwhile, our community is so walkable - our Walkscore is 97 - just a few blocks to the Amazon campus and to Seattle's best little hangouts, restaurants, cafes and bars.", 'Floor Plan Details', 'Name: Studio E', 'Studio / 1 Bathrooms', '423 Sq.', 'Ft.', '$1,725.00 - $2,159.00', 'Community Amenities', 'Smoke-free', "10 minute walk to Amazon's campus", 'Entertain and socialize with our clubroom kitchen', 'Compete or brush up on your skills with our billiards table', 'Controlled access parking garage', 'Easy access to I-5', 'Free Wi-Fi offered in social spaces', 'Fully equipped fitness center with cardio, machines, and free weights', 'Nearby Zip Car locations', 'Only minutes to light rail, public transportation and Seattle Streetcar', 'On-site recycling program', 'Private rooftop garden with amazing views and multiple social hang-out zones', 'State-of-the-art laundry facility', "Walk to Belltown's restaurants, bars, cafes and shopping", 'On-site convenience store', 'On-site hair salons', 'On-site post office', 'On-site fitness trainer', 'On-site smoothie shop', "99 Walk Score - Walker's Paradise", 'Spin cycles with On Demand training awaits', 'Change of pace in our social lounge', 'Enjoy grilling with stunning Seattle views from the rooftop', 'Work or play in our business center', 'Recipient of the 2020 ApartmentRatings Top Rated Award', 'Property Contact', 'show contact info', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
